Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.70,0:00:20.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,《比利小子》前情提要\N{\rYUANWEN}Previously on "Billy the Kid"...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.58,0:00:21.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这家商店关门歇业了\N{\rYUANWEN}This store is no longer trading.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.08,0:00:23.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,大家都回家吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Please go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.45,0:00:25.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,布雷迪警长 我认为\N{\rYUANWEN}Sheriff Brady, I do not believe
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:26.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你不是在伸张正义\N{\rYUANWEN}you are serving justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.13,0:00:28.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,而是在为浩世为虎作伥\N{\rYUANWEN}You're only workin'for the House.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.79,0:00:29.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们可以为所欲为 小子们\N{\rYUANWEN}We do what we want, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.00,0:00:31.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们就是法律\N{\rYUANWEN}We are the fuckin' law.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.09,0:00:33.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们有枪\N{\rYUANWEN}We've got the guns,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.92,0:00:36.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,浩世就是林肯的地标\N{\rYUANWEN}and the House is a fuckin' institution.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.30,0:00:37.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,林肯越来越危险了\N{\rYUANWEN}It's gettin'real dangerous here in Lincoln.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.01,0:00:40.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你必须每天练习\N{\rYUANWEN}You gotta practice every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.76,0:00:42.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,事态很快会变糟\N{\rYUANWEN}This thing's about to get real messy real quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.27,0:00:43.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,布雷迪警长带着武装队\N{\rYUANWEN}Sheriff Brady and a posse
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.52,0:00:45.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,明早会到这里\N{\rYUANWEN}will arrive here in the morning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:47.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,为你送达查封令 没收你所有的马匹\N{\rYUANWEN}to serve you with a writ and seize all of your horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.10,0:00:49.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你应该捍卫牧场\N{\rYUANWEN}You should defend the ranch.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.61,0:00:51.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,保护你的财产\N{\rYUANWEN}Protect your property.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.48,0:00:54.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不想让这些人为我丧命\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't want any of these people to die for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.94,0:00:56.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们已经开战了 继续跟他们硬刚\N{\rYUANWEN}We're at war. We gotta fight'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.78,0:00:58.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我在想 也许可以趁警长没来\N{\rYUANWEN}I was just thinking that we could move the horses
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.28,0:00:59.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,把马匹转移走\N{\rYUANWEN}before the sheriff gets here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.20,0:01:02.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们黎明时分 从汤斯顿的牧场逃走\N{\rYUANWEN}They struck out from Tunstall's ranch around dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.49,0:01:03.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们沿着他们的踪迹\N{\rYUANWEN}Picked up their trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.95,0:01:07.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,最后追踪到汤斯顿市人\N{\rYUANWEN}Finally, we tracked down Tunstall himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.62,0:01:08.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们让他投降\N{\rYUANWEN}We told him to surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.13,0:01:11.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他向我们开枪 我们只好回击\N{\rYUANWEN}He fired at us, and we fired back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.17,0:01:14.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我以母亲的坟墓起誓\N{\rYUANWEN}I swear on my mother's grave,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.46,0:01:16.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我会杀了所有害死你的人\N{\rYUANWEN}I will kill every man involved in your murder,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.05,0:01:20.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,死也在所不惜 愿上帝保佑我\N{\rYUANWEN}or die myself in the attempt, so help me God.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.35,0:01:22.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我必须把法律掌握在自己手中\N{\rYUANWEN}I have to take the law into my own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.31,0:01:23.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你告诉我你已经改了\N{\rYUANWEN}- You told me you changed. -
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.02,0:01:26.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,下次再见你 就是在通缉令上了\N{\rYUANWEN}The next time I'll see your face will be on a"Wanted"poster.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.56,0:01:29.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,希望大家理解 如果以暴制暴\N{\rYUANWEN}But I want you all to appreciate that if you respond
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.56,0:01:32.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,以牙还牙\N{\rYUANWEN}to this act of violence in kind,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.48,0:01:34.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所有人都会鲜血横流\N{\rYUANWEN}then there will be a lot of bloodshed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.24,0:01:42.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那就让鲜血横流吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Then let there be bloodshed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.34,0:03:24.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,事情一发不可收拾了 比利\N{\rYUANWEN}Things are moving really fast, Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:26.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所有监管者 都被贝克和莫顿的律师\N{\rYUANWEN}The Regulators have all been charged with the murder
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:27.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,指控为谋杀\N{\rYUANWEN}of Baker and Morton.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:31.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你们现在是通缉犯了 一露面就会被逮捕\N{\rYUANWEN}You're wanted men now, and you'll be arrested on sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.27,0:03:32.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们应该暂时离开林肯县\N{\rYUANWEN}We should quit Lincoln County for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:36.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不 我仇还没报完\N{\rYUANWEN}No. I'm not finished here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.81,0:03:39.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-还没结束  -墨菲和他的同伙\N{\rYUANWEN}There's more. I've been ordered to appear
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:41.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,指控我捏造虚报帐目 侵吞国家资金\N{\rYUANWEN}before the district court to face those charges
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.53,0:03:42.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,地方法院命令我\N{\rYUANWEN}of false accounting and embezzling state funds
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:44.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,出庭对质\N{\rYUANWEN}that Murphy and his pals cooked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.95,0:03:46.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-你要去吗  -这是我唯一\N{\rYUANWEN}You gonna go? - It's the only chance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:48.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,为自己正名的机会 那些指控\N{\rYUANWEN}I have to clear my name. The charges against me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:50.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,过于荒谬 陪审团不可能认定我有罪\N{\rYUANWEN}are so ridiculous, no jury would ever convict me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.12,0:03:52.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我会无罪释放\N{\rYUANWEN}I'II walk out of there a free man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:54.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那你好好保重\N{\rYUANWEN}Just be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:15.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,开庭日期是什么时候\N{\rYUANWEN}When's the court date?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:18.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,月底\N{\rYUANWEN}It's the end of the month.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:20.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,陪审团很可能不会认定麦克斯温有罪\N{\rYUANWEN}There's a good chance the jury won't find against McSween.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:24.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-你知道的吧  -我知道\N{\rYUANWEN}You know that, right? - I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.86,0:04:28.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们得确保他没机会站上法庭\N{\rYUANWEN}We gotta make sure that he doesn't have his day in court.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:30.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,要怎么做到呢\N{\rYUANWEN}How do we do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.49,0:04:34.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,麦克斯温总要过来出庭的 对吧\N{\rYUANWEN}McSween's gotta come out of hiding to attend court, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:37.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们就让布雷迪警长半路把他抓住\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, then, we'll just get Sheriff Brady to apprehend him
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:39.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,给他签发逮捕令\N{\rYUANWEN}before he gets there, serve him with a warrant for his arrest,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:41.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,然后把他扔进监狱\N{\rYUANWEN}then throw him in jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:45.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他被关起来之后\N{\rYUANWEN}And once he's all locked up,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:47.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,找一个我们自己的法官审理\N{\rYUANWEN}we'll just get one of our own judges to make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:51.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,确保判他有罪 直接吊死他\N{\rYUANWEN}he's convicted, and then we'll just hang him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:58.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,妙 妙啊\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:05:00.23,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但如果比利和那些监管者\N{\rYUANWEN}But then what if Billy and the Regulators
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:02.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-跟他一起来呢  -那他们都会被捕\N{\rYUANWEN}ride into town with him? - Well, then they'll all
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.86,0:05:05.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,并被一起投入监狱\N{\rYUANWEN}be arrested and thrown in jail themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.36,0:05:07.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,总之\N{\rYUANWEN}Anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:09.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们不敢来的\N{\rYUANWEN}they wouldn't dare.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:13.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,即便如此 我们也得早做安排\N{\rYUANWEN}Even so, I do think we need to arrange a little something
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.95,0:05:15.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不能在那天让监管者\N{\rYUANWEN}on the day that makes it more difficult
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.87,0:05:17.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有插手的机会\N{\rYUANWEN}for the Regulators to intervene.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.08,0:05:20.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比如说什么\N{\rYUANWEN}Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:28.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我有个主意\N{\rYUANWEN}I've got an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:55.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有件事\N{\rYUANWEN}So, there's something
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:58.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我想跟你讨论一下 萨图尼诺\N{\rYUANWEN}I wish to discuss with you, Saturnino.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.41,0:06:01.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是时候扩大浩世的\N{\rYUANWEN}It is time to promote the vigor
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.09,0:06:04.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,影响力和经济实力了\N{\rYUANWEN}and the economic strength of the House.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:06.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,除掉汤斯顿之后\N{\rYUANWEN}With Tunstall out of the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.46,0:06:08.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,林肯尽在我们掌握\N{\rYUANWEN}we've the monopoly in Lincoln now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:10.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们要趁热打铁\N{\rYUANWEN}We need to take advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.30,0:06:11.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们要吸引新顾客\N{\rYUANWEN}We need to pull in new customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:15.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以 我建议在镇上办个小节日\N{\rYUANWEN}So, I'm suggesting that we have a little festival in the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:17.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我需要你的帮助\N{\rYUANWEN}And I need your help with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.68,0:06:20.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,想想看 广场中心的赛马比赛\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm imagining horse races in the center of the Plaza,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:22.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,斗鸡表演\N{\rYUANWEN}rooster fights,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:24.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,跳着方丹戈 音乐环绕\N{\rYUANWEN}fandangos, and there'll be music, and.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.15,0:06:28.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,杰西和他手下可以负责安保\N{\rYUANWEN}Jesse and his men- - they'll do security.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:31.95,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,听起来很有趣吧\N{\rYUANWEN}That sounds like fun, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:33.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,日期订好了吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Which date?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:35.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我在想 可以定在\N{\rYUANWEN}I was thinking that we might do it
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.87,0:06:38.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,本月的最后一天\N{\rYUANWEN}the last day of the month.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.71,0:06:42.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,麦克斯温的案子就在那天 对吗\N{\rYUANWEN}The day of the McSween court case, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.63,0:06:45.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\rYUANWEN}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:52.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那就尽情狂欢吧 朋友\N{\rYUANWEN}Bring on the festivities, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:54.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好\N{\rYUANWEN}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:27.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,祝我好运吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Wish me luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.84,0:07:36.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我得跟在他们后面\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm gonna follow them,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:38.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,确保他能活着到达\N{\rYUANWEN}just to make sure he gets there alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:07:58.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\rYUANWEN}- I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:06.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是布鲁尔\N{\rYUANWEN}It's Brewer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:08.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是布鲁尔\N{\rYUANWEN}It's Brewer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:17.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我马不停蹄地就来了\N{\rYUANWEN}I came as soon as I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:19.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我认识的一个副警长告诉我\N{\rYUANWEN}One of the sheriff's deputies I got friendly with
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:21.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,麦克斯温将被以谋杀从犯\N{\rYUANWEN}told me that McSween is gonna be served with a warrant
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.14,0:08:23.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,的罪名逮捕\N{\rYUANWEN}for accessory to murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:25.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,怎么 他连法庭都不能上了吗\N{\rYUANWEN}What, so he doesn't even make it to the court?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:27.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不 他告诉我朋友 等麦克斯温进了监狱后\N{\rYUANWEN}No. He told my friend that once McSween is behind bars,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:29.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他会立刻被判有罪 并处以绞刑\N{\rYUANWEN}he'll be found guilty and hanged.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:32.23,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他预计啥时候能到法院\N{\rYUANWEN}What time's he due in the courthouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.44,0:08:34.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,11点\N{\rYUANWEN}11 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.49,0:08:38.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不好\N{\rYUANWEN}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:45.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不能让这种事发生\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, that's not happenin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.83,0:08:47.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我要去林肯 谁跟我一起\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm riding into Lincoln. Who's comin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:49.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你打算做什么\N{\rYUANWEN}What are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:51.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我打算阻止布雷迪\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm gonna stop Brady.
