Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.38,0:41:34.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他在哪里 嗯\N{\rYUANWEN}Where is he? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.59,0:41:35.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,杰西\N{\rYUANWEN}Jesse!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.65,0:41:55.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那个英国人我不是我杀的\N{\rYUANWEN}I didn't kill the Englishman.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.61,0:41:59.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你还有机会 杰西\N{\rYUANWEN}You still have a chance, Jesse.
