Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.89,0:43:02.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你是 我们的新警长\N{\rYUANWEN}So, our new sheriff.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.93,0:43:06.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,请进 来喝一杯吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Come on in. Have a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.78,0:43:16.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,见到你很高兴\N{\rYUANWEN}It's good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.40,0:43:18.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我知道卡特伦先生面试了很多候选人\N{\rYUANWEN}I know Mr. Catron interviewed many candidates.
